The paper discusses a cryptographic construction for biometric authentication, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of LDPC codes for this purpose suggests a focus on information theory (cs.IT) and error-correcting codes (cs.CC). The paper also mentions the use of biometric data, which could be related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM).
